description:
Download “Classic Music Ringtones” and get the BEST collection of ringtones from classical composers

YOUR FAVORITE COMPOSERS and ARTISTS
Bach, Barber, Beethoven, Bizet, Boccherini, Chopin, Copland, Delibes, Dukas, Elgar, Fucik, Gershwin, Grieg, Handel, Jenkins, Khachaturian, Liszt, Mendelssohn, Mozart, Mussorgsky, Offenbach, Orff, Pachelbel, Ponchielli, Ravel, Rimsky-Korsakob, Strauss, Tchaikovsky, Vivaldi, Wagner.

Casual fans will recognize these classics from television, movies, cartoons, and commercials while purists will appreciate range and depth of the collection.

FOUR WAYS TO ENJOY
* Ringtones – Personalize your phone with a different ringtone.
* Caller ID – Have a little fun and assign different ringtones for mom, dad, and friends.
* Alarm Tones – Wakeup each morning to a custom tone. 
* Text Alerts – Stop missing important text messages.
